==English==

===Noun===
'''chaffinch''' (''plural'' '''[[chaffinches]]''')

#A small [[passerine]] bird, ''Fringilla coelebs'', of the [[finch]] family.
#In Northern [[British]] slang, '''chaffinch''' is a term for [[anus]].

